    D6A --> D6Why

    D7Q --> D7A
    D7A --> D7Why

    subgraph D8["Decision 8: MCP Spec Compliance"]
        D8Q["How to ensure<br/>tool discovery works?"]
        D8A["get_tools/0 override<br/>+ Dockerfile timeout patch"]
        D8Why["ExMCP DSL uses snake_case atom keys<br/>(:input_schema, :display_name, :meta).<br/>MCP spec requires camelCase strings.<br/>Override normalizes keys for clients.<br/>Dockerfile patches 10s→120s timeout<br/>for long-running tools like reindex."]
    end

    D8Q --> D8A
    D8A --> D8Why

